"'''Venus'''" is a 1969 song by the [[Netherlands|Dutch]] band [[Shocking Blue]] which the group took to number one in the U.S. and five countries across Europe in 1970. Notably covered by girl group [[Bananarama]], the song returned to number one in the U.S. and topped the charts in six other countries around the world in 1986. The composition has been featured in numerous films, television shows and commercials, and covered dozens of times by artists around the world.
